<h2>Known source inconsistency</h2>
<p>ACC's <a href="https://offices.austincc.edu/operations-and-public-affairs/public-affairs/annexation/" target="_blank">annexation page</a> still lists $361/credit hour out-of-district and a two-year total of $21,660. This is inconsistent with the <a href="https://admissions.austincc.edu/tuition-costs/" target="_blank">current tuition page</a>, which shows $286/credit hour. All figures on this site use the current tuition page as the authoritative source. We have flagged the inconsistency to ACC.</p>

